The Earth is in danger.
Global warming or a collision with a killer asteroid.
Caravans of spacecraft with Earthlings on board are on their way, looking for a replacement planet.
To save humanity, the central question is how to keep our species in weightless conditions or on a given replacement planet.
I don't think the selection is that big.
