As promised, I've partially curbed my activities.
For example, the travel agent will be my deputy in the spring.
The people would want me to be the Samaritan who saves the republic.
But I need to make a living, too.
How much did you take per month as a businessman?
Two hundred to 400 thousand, which I'm taking.
And if I were president, I'd shut down my business.
